(1, 'Jean', '1 - Bienvenue en Alaska', '<h1>Ah, yes! John Quincy Adding Machine. He struck a chord with the voters when he pledged not to go on a killing spree.</h1> <p>You seem malnourished. Are you suffering from intestinal parasites? The alien mothership is in orbit here. If we can hit that bullseye, the rest of the dominoes will fall like a house of cards. Checkmate.</p> <p><em>Morbo will now introduce tonight\'s candidates&hellip; PUNY HUMAN NUMBER ONE, PUNY HUMAN NUMBER TWO, and Morbo\'s good friend, Richard Nixon.</em>&nbsp;When the lights go out, it\'s nobody\'s business what goes on between two consenting adults.</p> <h2>We\'re rescuing ya.</h2> <p>Shut up and get to the point! When the lights go out, it\'s nobody\'s business what goes on between two consenting adults. I barely knew Philip, but as a clergyman I have no problem telling his most intimate friends all about him.</p> <ol> <li><span style=\"color: #000000; background-color: #bfedd2;\">You\'ve killed me! Oh, you\'ve killed me!</span></li> <li><span style=\"color: #000000; background-color: #bfedd2;\">Spare me your space age technobabble, Attila the Hun!</span></li> <li><span style=\"color: #000000; background-color: #bfedd2;\">Man, I\'m sore all over. I feel like I just went ten rounds with mighty Thor.</span></li> </ol>', '2020-07-31 20:35:03', '2020-07-31 20:35:03', 1, '/img/img-chapter-1.png'),
(2, 'Jean', '2 - Aller simple ?', '<h3>I\'m sorry, guys. I never meant to hurt you. Just to destroy everything you ever believed in.</h3> <p>All I want is to be a monkey of moderate intelligence who wears a suit&hellip; that\'s why I\'m transferring to business school! Oh right. I forgot about the battle. Meh. I could if you hadn\'t turned on the light and shut off my stereo.</p> <ul> <li>Shut up and get to the point!</li> <li>Fry, we have a crate to deliver.</li> <li>You\'ve killed me! Oh, you\'ve killed me!</li> </ul> <p>Doomsday device? Ah, now the ball\'s in Farnsworth\'s court! In your time, yes, but nowadays shut up! Besides, these are adult stemcells, harvested from perfectly healthy adults whom I killed for their stemcells.</p> <p>Just once I\'d like to eat dinner with a celebrity who isn\'t bound and gagged. Oh, all right, I am. But if anything happens to me, tell them I died robbing some old man. OK, this has gotta stop. I\'m going to remind Fry of his humanity the way only a woman can.</p>', '2020-07-31 20:35:52', '2020-07-31 20:35:52', 1, '/img/img-chapter-2.png'),
(3, 'Jean', '3 - Une vie plus simple', '<p>Just once I\'d like to eat dinner with a celebrity who isn\'t bound and gagged. Oh, all right, I am. But if anything happens to me, tell them I died robbing some old man. OK, this has gotta stop. I\'m going to remind Fry of his humanity the way only a woman can.</p> <p>Look, everyone wants to be like Germany, but do we really have the pure strength of \'will\'? We\'re rescuing ya. Good man. Nixon\'s pro-war and pro-family. Your best is an idiot! I can explain. It\'s very valuable.</p> <p>Bite my shiny metal ass. Aww, it\'s true. I\'ve been hiding it for so long. You mean while I\'m sleeping in it? I videotape every customer that comes in here, so that I may blackmail them later. Fry! Quit doing the right thing, you jerk!</p> <p>Bender, hurry! This fuel\'s expensive! Also, we\'re dying! What kind of a father would I be if I said no? Guards! Bring me the forms I need to fill out to have her taken away! Why, those are the Grunka-Lunkas! They work here in the Slurm factory.</p> <p>Oh Leela! You\'re the only person I could turn to; you\'re the only person who ever loved me. I saw you with those two \"ladies of the evening\" at Elzars. Explain that. As an interesting side note, as a head without a body, I envy the dead.</p> <p>Wow! A superpowers drug you can just rub onto your skin? You\'d think it would be something you\'d have to freebase. But existing is basically all I do! Tell them I hate them. You\'re going to do his laundry?</p> <p>I\'m just glad my fat, ugly mama isn\'t alive to see this day. Now, now. Perfectly symmetrical violence never solved anything. File not found. Professor, make a woman out of me. She also liked to shut up!</p> <p>Good man. Nixon\'s pro-war and pro-family. Incidentally, you have a dime up your nose. Please, Don-Bot&hellip; look into your hard drive, and open your mercy file! Leela, are you alright? You got wanged on the head.</p> <p>Bender?! You stole the atom. Pansy. Really?! OK, if everyone\'s finished being stupid. Yes! In your face, Gandhi!</p> <p>Now, now. Perfectly symmetrical violence never solved anything. No. We\'re on the top. Oh, you\'re a dollar naughtier than most. Ok, we\'ll go deliver this crate like professionals, and then we\'ll go ride the bumper cars.</p>', '2020-07-31 20:39:11', '2020-08-13 16:51:40', 1, '/img/img-chapter-3.png'),
